gomodel:SYNGO_89  a       owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099059 replaced by GO:0048787" , "Rationale: PMCA1 is highly enriched in docked vesicles / active zone membrane fractions.\nSimilar ratio found for PMCA2 in the same paper.\n\n18/01/2017 Pim Note\n- Because enriched in AZ and not in free SV AT2B1 is presumably localized to the AZ membrane, not in SVs.\n- protein has TM domains. Experimental description: To isolate docking complexes from rat brain, we first prepared synaptosomes and subjected them to limited proteolysis to dissociate pre- and postsynaptic membranes (Figure 1A). p. 286" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
